        <h3><a href="/questions/478137/proving-y-ax-b-given-correlation-coefficient-rhox-y-1" class="question-hyperlink">Proving $Y = aX + b$ given correlation coefficient $|\rho(X, Y)| = 1$</a></h3>
        <div class="excerpt">
